title: 'Worth buying during offers!'
body: I bought it during Independence day offers in just Rs.1599/- and it's worth buying. Best in this price range in the category of hard trolley. It has inner lining with clips and separator for upper part too. Four wheels with 360degree rotation. If we pack properly more items can fit in. Moreover, it came properly packed inside the cartoon. Happy customer :)
